    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in wonderful shape! It runs smoothly, looks great, and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve really loved driving this one, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. Perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend getaway\u2014come take a look!",
