    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the S54B32 high-revving inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has undergone critical preventive maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment to ensure optimal valvetrain harmonics. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides precise engagement, complemented by a variable M differential lock for superior traction during corner exit. The suspension geometry remains true, featuring refreshed bushings and a rigid chassis that delivers communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. Recent cooling system service includes a high-flow water pump and aluminum thermostat housing. Rolling on a staggered set of Style 67 wheels with high-performance compound tires, this M3 is mechanically sorted and ready for spirited application.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Maintenance up to date. Reliable engine. Minor cosmetic wear. Ready to drive.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
