      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still has plenty of life left? I'm parting with my car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs smooth, and has been well-loved over the years. It's perfect for someone who wants a quality vehicle without the 'brand new' price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 29800.0,
