      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3, a true pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, maintaining its signature neutral handling and telepathic steering feedback. While the aesthetics reflect its status as a dedicated driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain is robust, providing the high-frequency induction note and balanced dynamics expected of an M-division icon.",
